{"tid":1100911,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如果今晚巴塞作客贏到曼聯兩球以上 我即刻為大家唱出我首名曲","createTime":"2019-04-10T17:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T18:43:16.000Z","uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e7e153f6d063fca5d65fd83b69d63ab1f1413fb","tid":1100911,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T17:13:23.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 巴塞作客要贏王者獌真係冇乜可能<br />\n首先蘇亞雷斯已經三年歐戰冇入球<br />\n然後古天奴水貨一名唔使多講<br />\n丹比利 剩係得速度 我曼牙young防能死佢<br />\n美斯更加唔使講 八強打後隱形是常識吧<br />\n得返嗰啲乜嘢拉傑迪影帝真係不入流<br />\n後防碧基太慢 廢閘唔想多提<br />\n個龍連德國正選都冇 廢能到<br />\n加上巴塞未試過喺奥脱福贏波<br />\n你話俾疤-6贏一球都叫OK<br />\n贏兩粒簡直係痴心妄想<br />\n贏三粒已經係大奇跡日<br />\n<br />\n如果巴塞作客贏到三球或以上<br />\n我立即為大家唱出我嘅名曲<br />\n垃圾朗拿度 得不到分數"},{"pid":"2cf295fb6dbcdc55e6979547038696883b50b84c","tid":1100911,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"喂喂喂 乜能野廢閘呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你講野小心d"},{"pid":"c0ad58af0a7b2576f306d3746b1d53d32219704f","tid":1100911,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cf295fb6dbcdc55e6979547038696883b50b84c","tid":1100911,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T17:16:03.000Z","msg":"喂喂喂 乜能野廢閘呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你講野小心d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T17:16:40.000Z","msg":"死能開吧 黑氣石"},{"pid":"38493c9741f9602622c8bd80ecccf842be39f49f","tid":1100911,"uid":75356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T17:19:32.000Z","msg":"咩唔入流呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce12b1e946f5aa4a61a2a226c857e5ac5772d57","tid":1100911,"uid":41434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T17:21:32.000Z","msg":"打隊垃圾獌都要燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /